{"tid":1264453,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：將達成“非常重大的”貿易協議","createTime":"2019-06-28T16:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T17:36:15.000Z","uid":66271,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d522ad67e7fd8126863071bd644f5060e61790","tid":1264453,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"在二十國集團(G20)峰會周五開幕之際，美國總統特朗普(Donald Trump)發出了與其他國家領導人和解的信號，稱美國將與印度和日本宣布&ldquo;非常重大的&rdquo;貿易協議。<br />\n特朗普此前與日本首相安倍晉三(Shinzo Abe)和印度總理莫迪(Narendra Modi)舉行了會晤，沒有就貿易協議提供細節。但特朗普對兩人的讚揚緩解了人們的擔憂，人們此前擔心他會在G20峰會上製造新的緊張。<br />\n本次峰會前，特朗普曾在Twitter上表示，印度最近宣布對美國徵收的關稅是&ldquo;不可接受的&rdquo;，&ldquo;必須撤銷&rdquo;。<br />\n但當他與莫迪坐在一起向記者發表簡短講話時，並沒有提到這個問題。特朗普說：&ldquo;我認為我們會繼續與印度和睦相處。&rdquo;&ldquo;我認為我們會宣布一些非常重大的消息，非常大的貿易協議。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4f4bbaf60d07a22530f45fd047d136c78374cf31","tid":1264453,"uid":103759,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國將與印度和日本宣布&ldquo;非常重大的&rdquo;貿易協議</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f81defaf6ed340300a48578c602ae5d6f580840","tid":1264453,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4bbaf60d07a22530f45fd047d136c78374cf31","tid":1264453,"uid":103759,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國將與印度和日本宣布&ldquo;非常重大的&rdquo;貿易協議</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"中國係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9624d2073e6213ac